      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/69c0132f60681.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/69c0133b2df5a.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a45a0fd94a63.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/69c0411460adb.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/69c041222faad.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; FIXED LIGHTING GLITCH&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Removal&lt;/em&gt;: Archived the original release of v1 of this mod&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Addition&lt;/em&gt;: Added a patch release for v1.1&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Bugfix&lt;/em&gt;: Fixed the lighting glitch&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://files.catbox.moe/2cok6c.png"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt; ♡&lt;/span&gt; &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/linkfilter?url=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FZdFazKAkpy&amp;follow=true"&gt;Join my Discord server for modding help, mod wip pics, mod requests and more &lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;♡&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;                           &lt;img src="https://files.catbox.moe/olqv20.png"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Part of the Ethereal Mod Pack,, &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;♡&lt;/span&gt; &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;This mod brings strawberry bushes to your game, because who doesn't love a good strawberry? ?&lt;br&gt;The strawberry bushes follows a growth cycle very similar to the original bushes in game and is meant to resemble the real life counterpart to strawberries and how they grow in real life! :)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;This mod uses sweet olive bushes for all stages apart from the final stage. So in summer when it's "fully grown" swap your bushes out for hibiscus bushes instead.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Red hibiscus bushes = red strawberries&lt;br&gt;Yellow hibiscus bushes = pink strawberries&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;♡ Vapecord IDs: &lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Sweet Olive Bush: 0097&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Hibsicus (Red): 0091&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Hibscus (Yellow): 0094&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;♡ Read the installation instructions &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/linkfilter?url=https%3A%2F%2Fkikifrommeadow.com%2F2025%2F12%2F31%2Fhow-to-install-my-mods-for-animal-crossing-new-leaf%2F&amp;follow=true"&gt;here.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://files.catbox.moe/do9i0h.png"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;CONFLICTS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;This mod will automatically conflict with any mod that is in this category. This is because flora/foliage mods all replace the same file.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;                          &lt;img src="https://files.catbox.moe/isgx7t.gif"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;CREDITS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;♡ &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/5316668"&gt;Goumaden &lt;/a&gt;- &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;For their tutorial and helping me with the lighting glitch this mod had at original release.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://files.catbox.moe/do9i0h.png"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Please do &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;NOT&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt; reupload my mods without my permission, this includes but not limited to: reposting/reuploading, editing/modifying, put under a paywall/reselling and/or claim ownership of my mods. This all falls under the Creative Commons License. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Do &lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;NOT&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt; download my mods/work under "modding services" and charge people for it. My mods will always be free to download and I'm more than happy to teach you how to install them if you're having trouble in doing so.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;If there are any issues please don't hestitate to contact me via Tumblr DMS &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/linkfilter?url=https%3A%2F%2Fkikifrommeadow.tumblr.com%2F&amp;follow=true"&gt;kikifrommeadow&lt;/a&gt; or alternatively comment under this post, I'll try and get back to you ASAP.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;♡&lt;/span&gt;  If you use my mods please tag me on social media so I can see ! I'd love to see your creations!&lt;b&gt; &lt;/b&gt; &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;♡&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://files.catbox.moe/9fl3kh.png"&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
