pan class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;"Jester's Cap"&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Pomni's Shirt:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt; This is a &lt;b&gt;QR Code&lt;/b&gt;. It should be the 3rd picture. If you don't see it i'll put it in the folder for you.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Pomni's Pants:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt; A recolor that gives you Pomni looking shorts. Replaces &lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;"Royal Shorts"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Pomni's Shoes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;: A recolor that (not super accurate) of the shoes. Replaces &lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;"Callie Shoes"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/linkfilter?url=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_nAMf5Xobys&amp;follow=true"&gt;(Video tutorial now available!) For a written version, use the tutorial inside the zipped folder if you need help on how to install.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;All I ask is that you download this mod for free personal use &lt;b&gt;ONLY&lt;/b&gt;, NOT commercial. &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;(Do not repost, resell, re-edit, claim ownership, or place behind a paywall.)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;b&gt;[&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&gt;Under Creative Commons License]&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt; (Please credit me by linking my mods if you ever use them for screenshots or for your mods.)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Thank you so much for shopping at my boutique! Stay glamorous.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;-Mikii&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;♡&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;---------------------------------------------------------------&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;**The Character "Pomni" from "The Amazing Digital Circus" is not made by me. This cosplay mod is fanart no copyright infringement is intended.**&lt;/i&gt;</description>
