      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a1bd147b2b1a.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a18cc3b89f0b.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a19fd9fdfe63.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a19fda31b1fa.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a1b702db9661.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a1b70d6083a8.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a1b70da63847.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a220614baa17.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a22061c0eec5.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a264f43d210d.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a264f5179550.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; Version 5&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Change&lt;/em&gt;: Added Claire&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Change&lt;/em&gt;: Added Jill&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;～～～～～ABOUT～～～～～&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;This mod reskins some villagers into Resident Evil characters.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Right now it is&lt;br&gt;KYLE ➞ LEON (wol10)&lt;br&gt;NATE ➞ CHRIS (bea05)&lt;br&gt;KABUKI ➞ WESKER (cat09)&lt;br&gt;RIZZO ➞ BIRKIN (mus09)&lt;br&gt;ZELL ➞ LUIS (der02)&lt;br&gt;LIONEL ➞ CARLOS (lon08)&lt;br&gt;FILBERT ➞ ETHAN (squ02)&lt;br&gt;ROLF ➞ KRAUSER (tig00)&lt;br&gt;WOLFGANG ➞ BILLY COEN (wol02)&lt;br&gt;MAPLE ➞ CLAIRE (cbr01)&lt;br&gt;DEIRDRE ➞ JILL (der04)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;this mod changes textures and English villager names. If you do not want the names to change, delete the "Script" folder.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;～～～～～HOW TO INSTALL～～～～～&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;To install, copy the "romfs" folder from the mod and paste it into the game's mods folder.&lt;br&gt;It should be mods/[game ID]/romfs&lt;br&gt;On emulator, you can get there by right clicking the game and selecting open ➞ mods location.&lt;br&gt;There is a Welcome Amiibo version included in the mod. Just use the romfs folder from that one instead if you are on Welcome Amiibo.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;～～～～～COMPATIBILITY&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;～～～～～&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Not compatible with other mods that replace any of the villagers that are replaced. One will overwrite. If you don't want it to overwrite another villager mod, you can delete the file for the character from this mod before pasting the romfs folder.&lt;br&gt;Because of how names work, one mod's names will overwrite all villager names. To have names of the villagers from all villager mods you have, use a hex editor. If you only have this villager mod or don't care about names, then you can ignore this.&lt;br&gt;You can see who your mods already replace by looking in mods/[game ID]/romfs/Npc/Normal/Model.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;～～～～～NOTES&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;～～～～～&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;New names have to be the same length as the original name. Because of that, Chris is called "Cris", Birkin is called "Birkn", Ethan is called "Winters", Krauser is called "Jack" (his first name), Billy is "Billy C.", Claire is "Clair", and Jill is "Jill V.". Everyone else has normal names.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;You can edit the textures in this mod as much as you want for your own game! But, please do not reupload this mod or claim credit. If you want to make and publish your own versions of the characters, that is okay, as long as you do not use my textures (even edited).&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Please tell me if there are any mistakes or problems in the mod. Thank you!</description>
